// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mlcBRr dodecagonal transition structure, 2023 by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mlcBzn square inscribe dodecagon circle

// related: https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mltBR8 dodecagonal 3-4 cylinder support
// related: https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dlcfzN square ring transition structure

// A dodecagonal prism structure for transition between voxel and cylinder:
// a cuboid containing a dodecagon prism containing an inscribed cylinder.
// Implemented by reflecting a part eight times (D8?) then repeating it vertically.

// tags: prism, cylinder, cuboid, dodecagon

